            ],
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The kobold scout creates a rudimentary trap on any square adjacent to it. This must be on a surface, such as a floor, wall, or ceiling. The trap activates the next time a creature moves adjacent to it. The creature takes 1d6 piercing damage and 1 persistent bleed damage with a DC 16 basic Reflex save. The trap is destroyed when activated or after 1 hour, whichever comes first. The scout typically carries enough raw materials to make one trap.",
            "traits": [
